   seeking to promote different moral objectives using positive emotions,
   which positive emotion will be the most effective for their respective
   campaigns? We demonstrate how the congruency between the moral domain of
   an emotion and the moral objective of an organization plays a role in
   influencing prosocial behaviors. Charities that seek to increase care in
